{{italic title}} '''''Prestige Bulletin''''' is a financial journal published monthly in [[South Africa]] since 1989.<ref>Experts give brilliant advice on your finances, ''Sunday Times Magazine'', June 28, 1992.</ref>
It covers [[investment]]s, [[financial market]]s, [[personal finance]], [[tax planning]] and entrepreneurship. ''Prestige Bulletin'' aims to be objective and does not promote specific investment products or accept advertising.<ref>''Prestige Bulletin'', Conditions and Indemnity, August 2007.</ref>
