'''Zhang Changhong''' ({{zh|s=张长虹}}, born 1958/59) is a Chinese entrepreneur, the chairman of DZH (formerly Shanghai Great Wisdom 上海大智慧), a financial data and software provider.
==Early life== Zhang Changhong was born in 1958/59, and educated at [[Suzhou University of Science and Technology]], from where he graduated in 1987.<ref name=Forbes/>
==Career== Zhang is chairman of DZH, which competes in China with [[Reuters]] and [[Bloomberg L.P.|Bloomberg]].<ref name=Forbes/>
==Personal life== He is married and lives in [[Shanghai]], [[China]].<ref name=Forbes/>
